        <item>
            <title>Sony 发表 2 支 G 系新镜头，400-800mm F6.3-8 + 16mm F1.8</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/sony-400-800mm-f638-16mm-f18/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-400-800mm-f638-16mm-f18</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/sony-400-800mm-f638-16mm-f18/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 10:51:34 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相机配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[16mm F1.8]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[400-800mm F6.3-8]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294476</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 近日推出两款全新 G 系列 E-Mount 镜头，分别为 FE 400-800mm F6.3-8 G OSS 超远摄变焦镜头及 FE 16mm F1.8 G 超广角定焦镜头。这两款镜头分别针对远摄及广角拍摄需求，适用于拍摄野生动物、运动、风景及影片制作。</p><h2>FE 400-800mm F6.3-8 G OSS：远距拍摄适用</h2><p>Sony FE 400-800mm F6.3-8 G OSS（SEL400800G） 为 G 系列 E-Mount 超远摄变焦镜头，焦距范围涵盖 400mm 至 800mm，并可搭配 1.4 倍及 2 倍增距镜，将焦距延伸至 1600mm。该镜头适合拍摄鸟类、野生动物、运动赛事及航空摄影。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294490" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image003-694x343.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image003-694x343.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image003.jpg 964w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294516" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294517" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image004-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image004-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image004.jpg 745w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294492" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image005-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image005-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image005.jpg 740w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image006-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image006-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image006.jpg 738w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image007-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image007-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image007.jpg 731w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>镜头采用内变焦设计，变焦过程中长度保持不变，减少重心转移对构图稳定性的影响。光学结构包含，六片超低色散（ED）镜片，用于减少色差，并在逆光环境下降低眩光与重影。11 片圆形光圈叶片，可提供柔和散景。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image008-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image008-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image008.jpg 742w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>对焦系统方面，镜头配备，两组线性马达对焦模组，可支援快速自动对焦及精准追踪。该镜头可与 Alpha 9 III 搭配使用，支援 120 fps 连拍。此外内置 Optical SteadyShot 光学防震，可减少手持拍摄时的震动，并可与具备影像稳定功能的 Alpha 机身结合使用，以提升稳定性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294520" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-4-421x580.jpg" alt="" width="421" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-4-421x580.jpg 421w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-4-scaled.jpg 653w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 421px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294521" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-5-421x580.jpg" alt="" width="421" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-5-421x580.jpg 421w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-5-scaled.jpg 653w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 421px" /></p><p>镜头具备防尘防潮设计，前镜片采用氟涂层，以提升耐用性及清洁便利性。此外，三脚架安装脚可旋转，提供横向及纵向构图支援。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image009-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image009-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image009.jpg 736w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 115px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;" colspan="2">发售资讯</td></tr><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">售价</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">港币 19,990 元</td></tr><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">公开发售日期</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">2025 年 3 月 13 日</td></tr><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">公开预售期</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">2025 年 2 月 27 日，至 3 月 11 日</td></tr><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;" colspan="2">预购礼遇：购买可获赠 BC-ZD1 双电池充电器（价值 HK$890），Sony Imaging Pro Support 会员可额外获得，一年星级服务（价值 HK$790）。</td></tr></tbody></table><h2>FE 16mm F1.8 G：轻量设计，适合广角摄影</h2><p>Sony FE 16mm F1.8 G（SEL16F18G） 为 E-Mount 超广角定焦镜头，适用于拍摄风景、建筑、星空及影片制作。该镜头配备 F1.8 大光圈，可在低光环境下使用，并可营造背景散景效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294508" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-694x509.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="509" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-694x509.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-scaled.jpg 1228w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294509" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-1-694x567.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="567" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-1-694x567.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-1-scaled.jpg 1102w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294510" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-2-694x567.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="567" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-2-694x567.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-2-scaled.jpg 1102w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294512" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-4-694x567.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="567" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-4-694x567.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-4-scaled.jpg 1102w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-6-675x580.jpg" alt="" width="675" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-6-675x580.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-6-scaled.jpg 1047w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 675px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294500" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image005-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image005-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image005-1.jpg 707w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294501" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image006-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image006-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image006-1.jpg 699w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294502" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image007-1.jpg" alt="" width="690" height="460" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294503" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image008-1.jpg" alt="" width="691" height="461" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294504" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image009-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image009-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image009-1.jpg 709w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294505" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image010-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image010-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image010-1.jpg 713w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>镜头内设两片进阶非球面（AA）镜片及三片 ED 镜片，用于减少色差与变形，提升影像解析度。最近对焦距离 0.15 米（自动对焦模式），手动对焦时可达 0.13 米，适用于特写拍摄。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294506" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image011.jpg" alt="" width="633" height="356" /></p><p>镜头搭载 XD 线性马达，提供快速自动对焦及追踪能力。专为 XD 马达开发的控制演算法可提升反应速度，降低震动与延迟。此外镜头支援 Alpha 相机内置的呼吸补偿功能，以减少对焦时的画面变化。镜头体积为 73.8 x 75 毫米，重量 304 克，设计轻巧便携。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294507" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image012.jpg" alt="" width="632" height="355" /></p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 115px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;" colspan="2">发售资讯</td></tr><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">售价</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">港币 6,490 元</td></tr><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">公开发售日期</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">2025 年 3 月 26 日</td></tr><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">公开预售期</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">2025 年 2 月 27 日，至 3 月 24 日</td></tr><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;" colspan="2">预购礼遇：购买可获赠 VF-67MPAM 多层镀膜保护滤镜（价值 HK$530），Sony Imaging Pro Support 会员可额外获得，一年星级服务（价值 HK$790）。</td></tr></tbody></table><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
